data.title: VMC Rooms, Park Buildings, Picnic Areas, and Outdoor Field Rentals
data.meta_description: Apply to rent rooms in Veterans Memorial Complex, park buildings, picnic areas and outdoor field spaces for fitness classes, youth sports, therapeutic small groups, faith based services, and any other reason.
data.text:
Step 5.Come to the Registration Office for Staff Assistance

The hours of operation for the Registration Office are:

Monday-Friday 8:00 am - 7:00 pm
